<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span> صحيح لغيره - <span class="c2">((الإرواء)</span>) <span class="c2">(١٩٦٥)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>